metadata.description:
25 ORIGINAL TOKENS

One physical carving has been crafted for each token holder. 
These will require a mailing address after purchase & are included in the price of each token. No hidden cost & you do not have to burn any tokens to redeem the physical. 

If you are not comfortable providing a personal mailing address at this time, please consider an alternative option, such as having it delivered to a Friend/Family/Dropbox.

Contact @P22535 directly on Twitter to provide an address. 
 
SYZYGY (1) token holders may also experience our Oncyber.io gallery:  
https://twitter.com/P22535/status/1620080499090944000

** Resale of any token from the SYZYGY (1) collection is not recommended at this time as it may not include a physical carving by P22535. Secondary listings should be considered as "NFT ONLY" & buyers beware.

@Mist8kofficial, @Muratpak, @ALCrego_
